-- Sevan Drilling in Talks to Extend Rig Options, Finansavisen Says
-- B y   S t e p h e n   T r e l o a r
-- 2011-12-20T07:34:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-20/sevan-drilling-in-talks-to-extend-rig-options-finansavisen-says.html
Sevan Drilling ASA is in talks with
Cosco Shipyard on extending options for the construction of two
additional rigs until the end of 2012, Finansavisen reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Scott Kerr.  Sevan Drilling will consider exercising the options after
it has secured contracts for two rigs currently under
construction, the Oslo-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Treloar at 
 streloar1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christian Wienberg at 
 cwienberg@bloomberg.net  